      <h1><a href="https://cryptokuchero.github.io/">cryptokuchero.github.io</a></h1>
      

      <h1 id="cryptokuchero">CryptoKuchero</h1>

<p>How to run a carpool based on BTC-Lightning.</p>

<h2 id="step-0-setup-your-lntxbot-ln-wallet">Step 0: Setup your lntxbot LN wallet</h2>

<p>Follow the instructions here: https://www.coingecko.com/buzz/how-to-stack-sats-with-lntxbot</p>

<h2 id="step-1-create-telegram-group-with-a-lightning-entrance-fee">Step 1: Create Telegram Group with a Lightning entrance fee</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Thanks to <a href="https://t.me/lntxbot">LnTxBot</a>, it is now possible to have everyone need to pay some sats to be able to continue on into a group.</li>
  <li>You can start this by adding lntxbot to the chat group and trying the command <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/toggle_ticket_100</code> which will make set it at 100 satoshis.</li>
  <li>The main advantage of this is to keep out people who do not have LN to begin with</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="step-2-craigslist-listing">Step 2: Craigslist listing</h2>

<p>Craigslist.org is <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Craigslist">one of the oldest classifieds</a> site. You can find “rideshare” listed under community tab. The link for rideshare. It allows for posting anonymously, by allowing the user to mask their email through the website.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Post on the rideshare community on craigslist about your carpool group and how to join on telegram. For example, if you are based in LA, you can go to https://losangeles.craigslist.org/d/rideshare/search/rid and post there.</li>
  <li>Include the instructions to setup a telegram-based lightning wallet with <a href="https://t.me/lntxbot">LnTxBot</a>.</li>
  <li>Please indicate “[LnCarpool]” on the headline so that it could be distinguished from the regular fiat-based.</li>
  <li>You can share what route you take going to your work and back.</li>
  <li>Remember to add much sats (satoshis) would you accept. It’s best to keep the fee lower than the usual offers so that people would be enticed.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="step-3-rideshare">Step 3: Rideshare!</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Pick up the passenger</li>
  <li>Talk about crypto while you enjoy the ridesharing.</li>
  <li>If the person hasn’t setup in Step 0, ask them to setup their wallet. You may offer to load it up if they do not have any way to get BTC.</li>
  <li>Enjoy the ride!</li>
  <li>Once you arrive at the destination, simply ask the passenger to reply to one of your messages with /tip <amount of="" satoshis="">. You can also opt to do a lightning invoice if you have other lightning wallets.</amount></li>
</ol>


      
